<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 235); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716292696075020675.png" title="1716292696075020675.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 195721.png" width="874" height="417" style="width: 874px; height: 417px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在这个充满活力和希望的季节里，我们经济管理学院</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">融媒体协会指导老师陈娴和杨磊、</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">融媒体协会全体成员、</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">23级宣传委员</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">于2024年5月15日</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">17:30在A10-304室</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; text-indent: 2.21428em;">齐聚一堂</span>，共同见证了融媒体协会全体大会的盛大召开。本次大会不仅是对过去一年工作的总结与回顾，更是对未来发展的规划与展望。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716292727489071344.png" title="1716292727489071344.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 195727.png" width="881" height="462" style="width: 881px; height: 462px;"/></span></p><p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716292808622087293.png" style="" title="1716292808622087293.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（融媒体协会会长舒慧燕进行工作总结及展望）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">大会伊始，融媒体协会会长作出了热情洋溢的发言。她首先感谢了全体成员在过去一年中的辛勤付出和无私奉献，对大家在融媒体事业中所取得的成绩给予了肯定。随后，会长也提出了工作中的不足：各部长要加强对部员的巩固培训，及时发现问题并积极改进，不断学习交流借鉴，增添创新元素。我们相信只要我们携手同行，奋力拼搏，必定会使蓬勃发展的协会绽放出更加夺目的光芒，我们也必定会在融媒体协会这个平台施展我们的抱负和才华，让我们的大学生活更加绚丽！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716292809089074089.png" style="" title="1716292809089074089.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（指导老师为上届干部颁发聘书）</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716292809183019378.png" style="" title="1716292809183019378.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">(指导老师为上届干事颁发聘书)</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716292809325050883.png" style="" title="1716292809325050883.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">(指导老师为</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">优秀干部、优秀部员颁发荣誉证书)</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716292809619049006.png" style="" title="1716292809619049006.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">(指导老师为优秀干部、优秀部员颁发荣誉证书)</span></p><p style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在大会进行过程中，融媒体协会对过去一年中表现突出的优秀个人和团队进行了表彰和奖励。这些优秀代表们在各自的岗位上发光发热，为融媒体事业的发展做出了突出贡献。他们的精神风貌和优秀品质将激励我们全体成员不断奋进、追求卓越。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 235);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716292925843061586.png" style="width: 881px; height: 477px;" title="1716292925843061586.png" width="881" height="477"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">(融媒体协会编辑部部长朱滢发言)</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716292926102004666.png" style="width: 885px; height: 470px;" title="1716292926102004666.png" width="885" height="470"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 227, 191);"></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">(融媒体协会信息部部长刘盈发言)</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716293584283078784.png" title="1716293584283078784.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 195815.png" width="885" height="547" style="width: 885px; height: 547px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（融媒体协会秘书部副部长周宁发言）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在随后的议程中，各部门负责人分别就本部门的工作进行了详细汇报。她们分享了各自在内容创作、图片拍摄、宣传推广等方面的经验和成果，同时也提出了对未来工作的规划和设想。大家纷纷表示我们是一个整体，各个部门是相互协调完成整个协会日常的运作，任何人在协会中发挥的作用都是缺一不可的。因此，如果大家能在今后认真负责，高质高效的工作工作，那么在未来我们的协会也会越做越好，得到更多人的认可，这也是我们身为一名媒体人的骄傲！</span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 235);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 37px; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716293096986041392.png" title="1716293096986041392.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 195819.png" width="891" height="465" style="width: 891px; height: 465px;"/></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（指导老师陈娴致辞点评）</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">指导老师首先回顾了过去一年融媒体协会的工作成果，这体现了对团队努力的认可和对工作成效的重视。通过总结，可以明确协会的优势和不足，为未来的发展提供方向。然后，指导老师对团队成员的付出和努力表示肯定和感谢，这种肯定能够激发团队成员的积极性和工作热情，增强团队的凝聚力和向心力。最后，指导老师期待在活动中看到各位的优秀表现。我们相信，在全体成员的共同努力下，一定会继往开来，扎实工作，不辜负全体师生的期望，为学院建设和发展做出应有的贡献，成为江软校园中一张亮丽的名片!</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: red; line-height: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716293220370015389.png" title="1716293220370015389.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 195709.png" width="911" height="535" style="width: 911px; height: 535px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（经济管理学院融媒体协会大合影）</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">本次融媒体协会全体大会的圆满落幕，不仅增强了我们的凝聚力和向心力，也为我们未来的发展奠定了坚实基础。我们将继续秉承“创新、协作、共赢”的理念，携手共进、共创美好未来！</span></p>